name: christmas-coding-challenge-2024
description: Welcome to my **Christmas Coding Challenge 2024** repo. This project is organized by the **[Women Coding Community](https://womencodingcommunity.com/)**. Through this challenge, I'm committing to solving one [LeetCode](https://leetcode.com/)  or [Northcoders](https://northcoders.com/) problem from the 1st to the 25th of December 2024.
